arStrings.szText: Hatred seeps from the jungles of Nahantu as the mysterious Realmwalkers spread Mephisto's influence across Sanctuary.

{c_highlight}{icon:bullet, 1}Realmwalkers:{/c} Slay these hulking demons to open a portal to a Seething Realm

{c_highlight}{icon:bullet, 1}Seething Realms:{/c} Choose your path and clear the dungeon to earn a Seething Opal

{c_highlight}{icon:bullet, 1}Seething Opals:{/c} Powerful consumables with your buff of choice

{c_highlight}{icon:bullet, 1}Corrupted Wells of Reflection:{/c} Find and cleanse these pools to earn greater Experience
